---
title: One-Sheet Sausage and Pepper Hoagies with Broiled Asparagus
description: This ballpark classic is perfect for baseball season! All the components cook in the oven on a baking sheet, leaving you with almost no cleanup. That way, you’ll be able to sit back and enjoy the game.
